overview: We went to DVD Magazine Vol.122 and divided the heated "Morship Game" into 3 teams and faced off in a round-robin battle! Reward for the winning team! !! And each of the three teams makes an original pizza full of individuality! !! Which team's pizza was the most delicious ??? At the end, Morning Musume.'21 is healed by playing with soap bubbles in nature. Morning Musume.'21 on location after a long absence. Enjoy Morning Musume.'21 DVD MAGAZINE! !! ("Sato Masaki" who could not participate in the location participates in the narration.)
title: Morning Musume.'21 DVD Magazine Vol.136
